Package: walker
Type: Package
Title: Efficient Bayesian Regression with Time-Varying Coefficients
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2017-06-22
Author: Jouni Helske
Maintainer: Jouni Helske <jouni.helske@iki.fi>
Description: Fully Bayesian regression models where the regression 
    coefficients are allowed to vary over "time", either as independent random 
    walks. Currently Gaussian and Poisson observations are supported. 
    All computations are done using Hamiltonian Monte Carlo provided by 
    Stan, using a state space representation of the model in order to marginalise 
    over the coefficients for efficient sampling.
License: GPL (>= 2)
